dashboard.definition:
{
  "title": "Sample Dashboard 5 \u2014 KPI Tiles (Value + Trend)",
  "description": "Four large KPI tiles demonstrating the v1.7.0 Value display + Trend features. Each tile is a single icon_library.icon_library viz. Covers all four valuePosition options, four valueFormat modes, threshold-driven value coloring, and both up_good and up_bad trend directions.",
  "defaults": {},
  "dataSources": {
    "ds_users": {
      "type": "ds.search",
      "options": {
        "query": "| makeresults count=48 | streamstats count as h | eval _time = relative_time(now(), \"-\" . tostring(48 - h) . \"h\") | eval value = 240 + h * 0.15 + (h * 3 % 7) - 3 | eval value = round(value * 1000, 0) | fields _time value"
      },
      "name": "Active users \u2014 hourly, last 48 h (K-scale)"
    },
    "ds_latency": {
      "type": "ds.search",
      "options": {
        "query": "| makeresults count=48 | streamstats count as h | eval _time = relative_time(now(), \"-\" . tostring(48 - h) . \"h\") | eval value = 220 - h * 0.9 + (h * 5 % 11) | eval value = round(value, 0) | fields _time value"
      },
      "name": "p95 latency ms \u2014 hourly, last 48 h"
    },
    "ds_errors": {
      "type": "ds.search",
      "options": {
        "query": "| makeresults count=48 | streamstats count as h | eval _time = relative_time(now(), \"-\" . tostring(48 - h) . \"h\") | eval value = 1.4 - h * 0.012 + (h * 7 % 5) * 0.05 | eval value = round(value, 2) | fields _time value"
      },
      "name": "Error rate % \u2014 hourly, last 48 h"
    },
    "ds_revenue": {
      "type": "ds.search",
      "options": {
        "query": "| makeresults count=48 | streamstats count as h | eval _time = relative_time(now(), \"-\" . tostring(48 - h) . \"h\") | eval value = 68000 + h * 210 + (h * 11 % 13) * 40 | eval value = round(value, 0) | fields _time value"
      },
      "name": "Revenue $ \u2014 hourly, last 48 h"
    }
  },
  "inputs": {},
  "visualizations": {
    "viz_canvas_bg": {
      "type": "splunk.rectangle",
      "options": {
        "fillColor": "#F5F5F7",
        "strokeColor": "transparent"
      }
    },
    "viz_header_title": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "backgroundColor": "transparent",
        "fontColor": "#1D1D1F",
        "fontFamily": "Helvetica",
        "fontSize": "extraLarge",
        "markdown": "# Sample 5 \u2014 KPI Tiles\n\n*Value + Trend (new in v1.7.0) \u00b7 each tile is a single `icon_library` viz*"
      }
    },
    "viz_header_note": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "backgroundColor": "transparent",
        "fontColor": "#6E6E73",
        "fontFamily": "Helvetica",
        "fontSize": "small",
        "markdown": "Every tile below is one `icon_library.icon_library` visualization \u2014 icon, big value, and trend arrow are rendered together. Data comes from a 48-row time-series (`\\| makeresults count=48 \\| streamstats count as h \\| ...`). The viz reads the **last** row for the current value and a row **N** bins back for the trend delta."
      }
    },
    "viz_shadow_users": {
      "type": "splunk.rectangle",
      "options": {
        "fillColor": "#E8E8ED",
        "strokeColor": "transparent"
      },
      "cornerRadius": [
        20,
        20,
        20,
        20
      ]
    },
    "viz_card_users": {
      "type": "splunk.rectangle",
      "options": {
        "fillColor": "#FFFFFF",
        "strokeColor": "#D2D2D7",
        "strokeWidth": 1
      },
      "cornerRadius": [
        20,
        20,
        20,
        20
      ]
    },
    "viz_users": {
      "type": "icon_library.icon_library",
      "dataSources": {
        "primary": "ds_users"
      },
      "options": {
        "backgroundColor": "transparent",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconName": "group",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconColor": "#06B6D4",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconSize": "0",
        "icon_library.icon_library.theme": "light",
        "icon_library.icon_library.showValue": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueField": "value",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valuePosition": "right",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueFormat": "abbreviated",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueColor": "#1D1D1F",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueSize": "0",
        "icon_library.icon_library.showLabel": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.labelText": "Active users (24 h)",
        "icon_library.icon_library.labelColor": "#6E6E73",
        "icon_library.icon_library.labelSize": "0",
        "icon_library.icon_library.showTrend": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.trendCompareBack": "24",
        "icon_library.icon_library.trendDirection": "up_good",
        "icon_library.icon_library.trendFormat": "percentage",
        "icon_library.icon_library.trendCaption": "vs 24 h ago"
      }
    },
    "viz_shadow_latency": {
      "type": "splunk.rectangle",
      "options": {
        "fillColor": "#E8E8ED",
        "strokeColor": "transparent"
      },
      "cornerRadius": [
        20,
        20,
        20,
        20
      ]
    },
    "viz_card_latency": {
      "type": "splunk.rectangle",
      "options": {
        "fillColor": "#FFFFFF",
        "strokeColor": "#D2D2D7",
        "strokeWidth": 1
      },
      "cornerRadius": [
        20,
        20,
        20,
        20
      ]
    },
    "viz_latency": {
      "type": "icon_library.icon_library",
      "dataSources": {
        "primary": "ds_latency"
      },
      "options": {
        "backgroundColor": "transparent",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconName": "speed",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconColor": "#06B6D4",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconSize": "0",
        "icon_library.icon_library.theme": "light",
        "icon_library.icon_library.showValue": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueField": "value",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valuePosition": "below",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueFormat": "integer",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueUnit": "ms",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueUnitPosition": "after",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueSize": "0",
        "icon_library.icon_library.showLabel": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.labelText": "p95 latency",
        "icon_library.icon_library.labelColor": "#6E6E73",
        "icon_library.icon_library.labelSize": "0",
        "icon_library.icon_library.showTrend": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.trendCompareBack": "1",
        "icon_library.icon_library.trendDirection": "up_bad",
        "icon_library.icon_library.trendFormat": "both",
        "icon_library.icon_library.trendCaption": "vs prev hour",
        "icon_library.icon_library.thresholdField": "value",
        "icon_library.icon_library.thresholdLow": "150",
        "icon_library.icon_library.thresholdHigh": "300",
        "icon_library.icon_library.thresholdDirection": "high_bad",
        "icon_library.icon_library.colorIcon": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.colorValue": "yes"
      }
    },
    "viz_shadow_errors": {
      "type": "splunk.rectangle",
      "options": {
        "fillColor": "#E8E8ED",
        "strokeColor": "transparent"
      },
      "cornerRadius": [
        20,
        20,
        20,
        20
      ]
    },
    "viz_card_errors": {
      "type": "splunk.rectangle",
      "options": {
        "fillColor": "#FFFFFF",
        "strokeColor": "#D2D2D7",
        "strokeWidth": 1
      },
      "cornerRadius": [
        20,
        20,
        20,
        20
      ]
    },
    "viz_errors": {
      "type": "icon_library.icon_library",
      "dataSources": {
        "primary": "ds_errors"
      },
      "options": {
        "backgroundColor": "transparent",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconName": "warning_amber",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconColor": "#06B6D4",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconSize": "0",
        "icon_library.icon_library.theme": "light",
        "icon_library.icon_library.showValue": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueField": "value",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valuePosition": "right",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueFormat": "two_decimals",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueUnit": "%",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueUnitPosition": "after",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueSize": "0",
        "icon_library.icon_library.showLabel": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.labelText": "Error rate",
        "icon_library.icon_library.labelColor": "#6E6E73",
        "icon_library.icon_library.labelSize": "0",
        "icon_library.icon_library.showTrend": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.trendCompareBack": "1",
        "icon_library.icon_library.trendDirection": "up_bad",
        "icon_library.icon_library.trendFormat": "percentage",
        "icon_library.icon_library.trendCaption": "vs prev",
        "icon_library.icon_library.thresholdField": "value",
        "icon_library.icon_library.thresholdLow": "0.5",
        "icon_library.icon_library.thresholdHigh": "1.0",
        "icon_library.icon_library.thresholdDirection": "high_bad",
        "icon_library.icon_library.colorIcon": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.colorValue": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.glow": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.glowColor": "#06B6D4",
        "icon_library.icon_library.glowSize": "8",
        "icon_library.icon_library.colorGlow": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.thresholdPulse": "critical"
      }
    },
    "viz_shadow_revenue": {
      "type": "splunk.rectangle",
      "options": {
        "fillColor": "#E8E8ED",
        "strokeColor": "transparent"
      },
      "cornerRadius": [
        20,
        20,
        20,
        20
      ]
    },
    "viz_card_revenue": {
      "type": "splunk.rectangle",
      "options": {
        "fillColor": "#FFFFFF",
        "strokeColor": "#D2D2D7",
        "strokeWidth": 1
      },
      "cornerRadius": [
        20,
        20,
        20,
        20
      ]
    },
    "viz_revenue": {
      "type": "icon_library.icon_library",
      "dataSources": {
        "primary": "ds_revenue"
      },
      "options": {
        "backgroundColor": "transparent",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconName": "payments",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconColor": "#06B6D4",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconSize": "0",
        "icon_library.icon_library.theme": "light",
        "icon_library.icon_library.showValue": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueField": "value",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valuePosition": "left",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueFormat": "thousands",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valuePrefix": "$",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueSize": "0",
        "icon_library.icon_library.valueColor": "#1D1D1F",
        "icon_library.icon_library.showLabel": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.labelText": "Hourly revenue",
        "icon_library.icon_library.labelColor": "#6E6E73",
        "icon_library.icon_library.labelSize": "0",
        "icon_library.icon_library.showTrend": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.trendCompareBack": "1",
        "icon_library.icon_library.trendDirection": "up_good",
        "icon_library.icon_library.trendFormat": "absolute",
        "icon_library.icon_library.trendCaption": "vs prev hour"
      }
    },
    "viz_section_how": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "backgroundColor": "transparent",
        "fontColor": "#1D1D1F",
        "fontFamily": "Helvetica",
        "fontSize": "large",
        "markdown": "## How the tiles above are configured"
      }
    },
    "viz_shadow_explain": {
      "type": "splunk.rectangle",
      "options": {
        "fillColor": "#E8E8ED",
        "strokeColor": "transparent"
      },
      "cornerRadius": [
        16,
        16,
        16,
        16
      ]
    },
    "viz_card_explain": {
      "type": "splunk.rectangle",
      "options": {
        "fillColor": "#FFFFFF",
        "strokeColor": "#D2D2D7",
        "strokeWidth": 1
      },
      "cornerRadius": [
        16,
        16,
        16,
        16
      ]
    },
    "viz_explain_md": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "backgroundColor": "transparent",
        "fontColor": "#1D1D1F",
        "fontFamily": "Helvetica",
        "fontSize": "small",
        "markdown": "**Tile 1 \u00b7 Active users** \u2014 `valuePosition: right` \u00b7 `valueFormat: abbreviated` (247.3 \u2192 **247.3K**) \u00b7 `trendCompareBack: 24` (vs 24 h ago).\n\n**Tile 2 \u00b7 p95 latency** \u2014 `valuePosition: below` \u00b7 `valueUnit: ms` \u00b7 `valueFormat: integer` \u00b7 `up_bad` trend \u00b7 threshold engine colors both icon and value.\n\n**Tile 3 \u00b7 Error rate** \u2014 `valuePosition: right` \u00b7 `valueUnit: %` \u00b7 `valueFormat: two_decimals` \u00b7 `up_bad` trend \u00b7 threshold engine pulses the glow red on critical.\n\n**Tile 4 \u00b7 Revenue** \u2014 `valuePosition: left` \u00b7 `valuePrefix: $` \u00b7 `valueFormat: thousands` (68000 \u2192 **$68,000**) \u00b7 `up_good` absolute trend."
      }
    },
    "viz_footer": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "backgroundColor": "transparent",
        "fontColor": "#6E6E73",
        "fontFamily": "Helvetica",
        "fontSize": "extraSmall",
        "markdown": "*Sample 5 \u00b7 showcases the v1.7.0 Value display + Trend features \u00b7 every tile is one `icon_library.icon_library` viz \u00b7 data is a 48-bin `\\| makeresults` time-series with slight up/down curves so the trend arrow shows a realistic delta.*"
      }
    }
  },
  "layout": {
    "globalInputs": [],
    "tabs": {
      "items": [
        {
          "label": "KPI Tiles",
          "layoutId": "layout_main"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "showTabBar": false
      }
    },
    "layoutDefinitions": {
      "layout_main": {
        "type": "absolute",
        "options": {
          "width": 1920,
          "height": 1240
        },
        "structure": [
          {
            "item": "viz_canvas_bg",
            "type": "block",
            "position": {
              "x": 0,
              "y": 0,
              "w": 1920,
              "h": 1240
            }
          },
          {
            "item": "viz_header_title",
            "type": "block",
            "position": {
              "x": 60,
              "y": 30,
              "w": 1200,
              "h": 90
            }
          },
          {
